DPIF_PointCloudSpherical_t Struct Reference

Point cloud definition in spherical coordinate system. More...

#include <dpif/dpif_pointcloud.h>

Data Fields

float range
 Range in meters.
 
float azimuthAngle
 Azimuth angle in degrees in the range [-90,90], where positive angle represents the right hand side as viewed from the sensor towards the scene and negative angle represents left hand side.
 
float elevAngle
 Elevation angle in degrees in the range [-90,90], where positive angle represents above the sensor and negative below the sensor.
 
float velocity
 Doppler velocity estimate in m/s. Positive velocity means target is moving away from the sensor and negative velocity means target is moving towards the sensor.
 

Detailed Description

Point cloud definition in spherical coordinate system.
